lyzing numbers. The custom KPIs let me focus on what truly matters. The platform is fast, reliable, and makes complex data easy to understand. I\u2019d recommend it to anyone who wants deeper insights without wasting time.",country:"Greece",membershipDuration:"1 year & 9 months",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"German M.",text:"Qualtrim is the best platform for investors out there. Allows you to check a company's fundamentals in a simple and intuitive way.",country:"Venezuela",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Nikita K",text:"Great platform, makes it way easier to track my current holdings and research any new potential investments. Plus, I think the AI features are far ahead of the competition.",country:"Canada",membershipDuration:"3 months",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Einar Z.",text:`Ever since starting to use Qualtrim I've had streamlined access to company fundamentals in a super clear and easy to use interface.
