The time period of using Qualtrim is the same time period I've grown the most as an investor, I get the facts, then I make the decision.`,country:"Sweden",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Alejandro G.",text:"Before Qualtrim, I was investing blindly, without paying attention to the fundamentals. After finally deciding to give it a try, I now use it every day. I explore companies, run valuations with the DCF calculator, among other things. For anyone considering it, I definitely recommend trying it out, as you even get a free one-month trial.",country:"Mexico",membershipDuration:"1 year",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Tran D.",text:"As a student who just begins investing, I\u2019m often overwhelmed when being presented lots of information. I find Qualtrim is very efficient at presenting key financial metrics, simple but easy to understand. Their transcript summary is my favourite, saving me time from reading while still providing core messages.",country:"Vietnam",membershipDuration:"1 year",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Maximilian S.",text:"I really value Qualtrim\u2019s intuitive interface and straightforward graphs. I\u2019ve been using it mainly to spot trends, screen for new investments, and analyze companies in more depth.",country:"Germany",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Dylan M.",text:"The main factor that drew me to Qualtrim was how easily it provides information. Before using it, I relied on YouTube videos and Yahoo Finance to learn about companies the process that often took hours, with no clear end point and a static number on a balance sheet didn\u2019t paint a full picture of a company\u2019s strength. When discussing stocks with friends, I noticed they too were spending hours watching content just to figure out which stocks they liked. With Qualtrim, however, a user can simply enter a ticker and quickly gain meaningful insights into whether a company is strong, cutting that process down to just minutes.",country:"Canada",membershipDuration:"2.5 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Nick L.",text:"Qualtrim is an integral part of my investment strategy as I used it on a daily basis. It is fast, easy to use, and I recommend it to all my friends and family. Looking forward to all the future updates!",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"4 years",showOnLanding:!0},{name:"Chris S.",text:"Qualtrim had provided me a simple, yet in-depth view of every stock fundamental I need to make an informed decision on my investments. This platform has helped grow my portfolio over 376% in the span of less than 3 years-not on its own, but by giving me the confidence to make informed investments. Without it, I probably wouldn't even beat the markets.",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"2.5 years",showOnLanding:!0},{name:"Peter A.",text:"I really love qualtrim ! I use it for 8 months now. You can see in one quick view how a company is doing. The kpi charts are usefull! The dcf calculator is a great tool, I use it a lot! Dip finder.. the portfolio analysis ..so many great things .Thank you sir!",country:"Netherlands",membershipDuration:"8 months",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Kevin L.",text:"Qualtrim delivers a stock research experience that stands head and shoulders above other platforms. Its robust KPI insights span every company on major indexes, offering a level of depth and clarity that\u2019s hard to match. The intuitive, user-friendly interface makes it effortless to navigate, whether you're diving into familiar stocks or discovering strong companies you might\u2019ve overlooked. I\u2019m genuinely excited to see how Qualtrim evolves over time\u2014it\u2019s already a game-changer.",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"9 months",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Peter A.",text:"Qualtrim has become a staple of my stock-finding and valuation process. The simplistic design and comprehensive coverage allows me to quickly evaluate companies and determine what is worth further research and investigation. This, combined with being able to track my own portfolio, has combined to a service that is difficult to beat on price or on capability.",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Ace S.",text:"I\u2019ve been using Qualtrim for nearly 2 years and I\u2019m very happy with the platform. The features are powerful and keep getting better, and I really appreciate how much Joseph integrates himself into updates and development to continuously improve the experience. As the leader of Stock Us. (\u0E2A\u0E15\u0E4A\u0E2D\u0E01\u0E2D\u0E31\u0E2A) Community Discord in Thailand, I can confidently say Qualtrim has been an invaluable tool for us. We highly recommend Qualtrim!",country:"Thailand",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Filip A.",text:`After trialing and testing more than 6-7 different stock analysis platforms out there, i settled with Qualtrim mainly due to:
Price
User Experience and ease of access from different devices
Level of actual detail and relevance to every bit of information displayed and served right at your fingertips.
Smooth and fast reactivity in every section of the app.

In the end, the reason i decided to stick with Qualtrim is, that after only about an hour or two checking it out, i realized that, what took me an hour or more to figure out on other platforms, took literal MINUTES on Qualtrim.
It's made my stock screening and research an order of magnitude faster compared to alternative tools.`,country:"North Macedonia",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Daniel M.",text:"Qualtrim has been the best tool I\u2019ve ever used for investing. Before using it, I was blindly picking companies without truly understanding their fundamentals. Now, this platform gives me all the information I need to make educated, confident decisions with my cash. Since using Qualtrim, I\u2019ve been able to pick better stocks and significantly increase my returns.",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"3 months",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Kevin D.",text:"I've been using Qualtrim since I started investing two years ago. While I'm still a relative beginner, combining Qualtrim with the principles of P. Lynch and C. Munger has helped me build a portfolio that has outperformed the market so far. The tool is intuitive, clear, and easy to use. Plus, the developers consistently add useful new features every quarter at no extra cost. Qualtrim has become an indispensable tool for managing my long-term portfolio.",country:"France",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Paulo A.",text:"As Chris Hohn puts it, \u201CVery few things matter, and most things don\u2019t matter at all.\u201D Quatrim ensures your attention stays on what genuinely matters.",country:"Portugal",membershipDuration:"5 months",showOnLanding:!0},{name:"Julian M.",text:"I have been using qualtrim for the better part of a year now maybe closer to two ever since I joined your discord. It is my one and only research app I use to read and analyze companies i\u2019m interested in. The way it\u2019s formatted is immaculate and extremely user friendly. It genuinely makes researching companies a breeze and actually enjoyable because I don\u2019t have to look up individual data points about a companies financials they may not all be on one site or app. It has everything I could possibly need and has benefitted my investing experience in so many ways. Truly a pleasure to use it and will never leave especially based on how much you update it and make it even better than I thought before like when you added the dip finder for example it\u2019s just so useful in so many facets to improve someone\u2019s portfolio. Huge fan Joseph thank you for everything, you truly changed my life financially and my mom\u2019s forever grateful to you, God bless man.",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Andr\xE9 P.",text:"My experience with Qualtrim is great, simple to use very well designed and with allot of information displayed in a way that makes it easy and appealing",country:"Portugal",membershipDuration:"2 years",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Jacky L.",text:"Qualtrim has really helped me become a better investor. I use it everyday to study company fundamentals and set entry prices using DCL calculator. Honestly, I can\u2019t recommend it enough\u2014it\u2019s an incredible tool for anyone who wants to grow into a long-term value investor.",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"6 months",showOnLanding:!1},{name:"Mian J.",text:"Qualtrim is a game-changer for investment research\u2014its intuitive design delivers high-impact insights through clean, visual dashboards that make key metrics instantly digestible. The AI-driven analysis dramatically cuts down research time, while the streamlined watchlist and portfolio tracking keep everything focused and easy to manage. It's a powerful tool for staying sharp in a fast-moving market.",country:"United States",membershipDuration:"4+ years",showOnLanding:!0}];var hc=(n,e,t,i)=>({"bg-white":n,"text-gray-900":e,"text-white/70":t,"hover:text-white":i}),fc=(n,e)=>({"bg-blue-500":n,"bg-gray-600":e}),Fi=(n,e)=>e.id;function pc(n,e){if(n&1){let t=Nn();f(0,"button",73),le("click",function(){let r=An(t).$implicit,o=N();return In(o.setActiveTab(r.id))}),b(1),g()}if(n&2){let t=e.$implicit,i=N();Ge("ngCl